    <item>
      <title>瑞银的埃尔莫蒂认为市场存在“脆弱因素”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/ubs-ermotti-sees-some-elements-of-fragility-in-markets-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[“波动幅度之大应该让人们仔细考虑是否要进行适当的分散投资，并仔细考虑投资方式。”瑞银集团首席执行官塞尔吉奥·埃尔莫蒂在苏黎世接受弗朗辛·拉夸采访时谈到了 8 月 5 日的抛售。“事实上，我们基本上在一两周内就收回了所有损失，在我看来，这不能被视为一个暂时的问题，”埃尔莫蒂补充道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/ubs-ermotti-sees-some-elements-of-fragility-in-markets-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 07:07:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威 1.7 万亿美元基金因科技股飙升而回报率达 8.6%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/norway-s-1-7-trillion-wealth-fund-returns-8-6-in-first-half</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于股市飙升，挪威 1.7 万亿美元的主权财富基金上半年回报率为 8.6%，即 1,380 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/norway-s-1-7-trillion-wealth-fund-returns-8-6-in-first-half</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 07:06:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非失业率创两年新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/south-africa-jobless-rate-at-two-year-high-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非第二季度失业率意外上升至2022年以来的最高水平，截至6月的三个月内达到33.5%，而上一季度为32.9%。南非统计局公布的数据显示，贸易和农业部门在此期间失业人数最多。彭博社的詹妮弗·扎巴萨贾在约翰内斯堡报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/south-africa-jobless-rate-at-two-year-high-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 06:39:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员充分预期英国央行今年将再降息两次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/traders-fully-price-two-more-boe-rate-cuts-this-year-after-cpi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在数据显示通胀增速低于预期后，交易员增加了对英国央行今年降息的押注，完全预期英国央行将再降息两次，每次降息25个基点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/traders-fully-price-two-more-boe-rate-cuts-this-year-after-cpi</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 06:33:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
